  "detailed_description": "<strong><br>Play through a collection of 3D fluid based casual puzzles. <br>Unlock new levels and freeplay mode as you complete objectives and earn rewards. <br>A simple casual experience based around having fun playing with fluids and physics.<br><br>At its core Habitatrix is a water physics puzzle game in which you place objects to control the flow of water (or lava) to achieve various level objects, such as preventing flooding inside a house, promoting plant growth in a desert, or protecting buildings from lava spewing from a volcano.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793200/extras/98a0d35575f0231adea4253170be95ca.avif?t=1718602492\" width=612 height=340 /></span><br><br>Each level throws new challenges your way with unexpected variations in the gameplay mechanics.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793200/extras/27e951b1504c19cd1d732d98d53d8734.avif?t=1718602492\" width=612 height=340 /></span><br><br>Simple controls let you flip and rotate falling objects with precision.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793200/extras/e9ab142cd22c601bc968a4050e41e173.avif?t=1718602492\" width=612 height=340 /></span><br><br>Play smart and quick to beat the goals within the allotted time to unlock more levels and free play mode.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2793200/extras/ee68481007543e0c6727e5706e996880.avif?t=1718602492\" width=612 height=340 /></span>",
